models.description: Hermes 2 Pro is an upgraded, retrained version of Nous Hermes 2, consisting of an updated and cleaned version of the OpenHermes 2.5 Dataset, as well as a newly introduced Function Calling and JSON Mode dataset developed in-house. This version excels at Function Calling, JSON Structured Outputs, and has improved on several other metrics, scoring 90% on function calling evaluation and 84% on structured JSON Output evaluation.
